The paper deals with object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves generating training samples with uniform IoU distribution, which is a technique related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the limitations of the Region Proposal Network (RPN), which is a component of object detection systems and can be considered a topic in computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper proposes a new method for improving the performance of object detection, which can be seen as a topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
